# Implementation Plan - Document & Lot Linkage

## Goal Description
1.  **Document Filenames**: Ensure "Analysis Report" and "Proof of Origin" files attached to a lot store and display their actual filenames.
2.  **Ship-Dump Linkage**: Update the "Parent Ship" selection to identifying ships by their **Lot Number** (ID) + Name, ensuring the link is clear and unambiguous.

